The Kenra Color Skill is a simple hands-free voice education experience for the professional stylist. Specially designed for the professional stylist to use at your color bar station. Alexa devices with screens have access to our educational video tutorials. 

COLOR CONVERSIONS – MIXING INSTRUCTIONS – PROCESSING TIMES – VIDEO TUTORIALS
